/**
 * Phaser Blend Modes to CSS Blend Modes Map.
 * 
 * @name Phaser.CSSBlendModes
 * @enum {string}
 * @memberof Phaser
 * @readonly
 * @since 3.12.0
 */

module.exports = [
    'normal',
    'multiply',
    'multiply',
    'screen',
    'overlay',
    'darken',
    'lighten',
    'color-dodge',
    'color-burn',
    'hard-light',
    'soft-light',
    'difference',
    'exclusion',
    'hue',
    'saturation',
    'color',
    'luminosity'
];
